column41: This is one of those courses that you get out of it what you put into it. I needed this course as a strategic sector rather than concentration requirement for ISAT, and as a result I don't think I got as much out of it as the rest of my group but I still learned an incredible amount on the top down process of software development. It is mainly with coding our program that I struggled most.
